{"tid":2267941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青山醫院男病人擅自離開仍未尋回","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:00:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bde07197a015584e2305af0946a7dcb67b07683c","tid":2267941,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"青山醫院今（2日）表示，一名41歲住院男病人今早由職員陪同到院外牙科診所覆診，其間擅自離開，院方已即時通知病人家屬，以及報警尋求協助，並會全力配合警方的搜索行動。<br />\n<br />\n該名男病人身高1.75米、中等身材、黑色短髮，當時身穿藍色外套及綠色長褲。青山醫院呼籲，公眾若發現該病人，致電3661 5810通知屯門警署報案室或致電青山醫院電話2456 7111。"},{"pid":"4a048b76500fe66b24a9a2ac786d81ed0fe8499b","tid":2267941,"uid":339272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"去左同公司開營火會個巴打"},{"pid":"234f7fb9b31ffcd9c632216adb0b6f6613202fe1","tid":2267941,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"我要返工呀， 唔入去度假了。"},{"pid":"3838332ea271e95c08723ee2dcd44822b1187b31","tid":2267941,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"青山ching 冇電話<br />\n你要行埋去搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d12aa026838b52fbe50ae213ec72c5bc99bd7b6","tid":2267941,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e553dbed9fdf910bfa5b726a29d44d2b01e7946","tid":2267941,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"今日出糧先至出左去執石頭啫"}]}